  "title": "Sales Associate (Part-Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>SALES ASSOCIATE (PART-TIME) – JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join our boutique team and deliver the relaxed luxury and charm of the French Riviera. We seek a polished, customer-centric Sales Associate who loves retail and wants to grow with a new flagship store.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please note the hourly rate is $15 per hour, with the salary range stated above denoted an estimated monthly range of average hours worked.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Perks 🤩</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Flexible working hours</li>\n  <li>Robust training across a comprehensive range of SKUs</li>\n  <li>Stable and competitive hourly rate</li>\n  <li>Fun, dynamic and driven team</li>\n  <li>Career growth and development (we're looking to GROW!)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities 🎯</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Sales &amp; Service</strong>: Deliver warm, professional service; build client loyalty; use brand selling techniques to meet targets.</li>\n  <li><strong>Store Presentation</strong>: Keep displays clean, stocked, and on-brand; restock promptly; assist with visual updates and stay product-savvy.</li>\n  <li><strong>Operations</strong>: Follow POS and cash procedures; handle returns and exchanges; maintain an orderly sales floor and stockroom.</li>\n  <li><strong>Team &amp; Brand</strong>: Uphold grooming standards, represent the brand at events, and contribute to a positive team culture.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements ✅</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Retail experience, fashion/lifestyle brands preferred, otherwise strong interest.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills and a genuine interest in helping customers.</li>\n  <li>Willingness to learn, take initiative, and work as part of a team.</li>\n  <li>Attention to detail and pride in maintaining high store standards.</li>\n  <li>Able to work flexible hours, including weekends and holidays.</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of POS systems and Microsoft Office is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Nearest MRT: HarbourFront</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About VILLA D’ÉTÉ</strong></p>\n<p>Inspired by the timeless elegance of the Côte d’Azur, VILLA D’ÉTÉ blends effortless glamour with contemporary resort fashion, artisanal fragrance, and curated lifestyle pieces. With boutiques in Cannes and Hainan, and a new flagship in Singapore, we celebrate beauty, craftsmanship, and the art of living well. Join us and bring Riviera sophistication to every guest.</p>",
