    "description": "<p>VILLA D’ÉTÉ is a luxury lifestyle brand inspired by the timeless elegance and artistic soul of the French Riviera. More than just a boutique, we offer an immersive escape into the refined, sun-drenched charm of southern France, blending effortless glamour with contemporary resort fashion, artisanal fragrances, and curated lifestyle experiences. Every collection is thoughtfully designed to evoke a sense of memory, sophistication, and emotional connection. With flagship boutiques in Cannes, France and Hainan Island, China, VILLA D’ÉTÉ is where elegance meets wanderlust. We invite passionate individuals to join us in shaping a brand that celebrates beauty, craftsmanship, and the art of living well.</p>",
